text: Khairul Anuar bin Mohamad (born 22 September 1991) is a Malaysian archer. Anuar Mohamad competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics, 2016 Summer Olympics, and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Khairul Anuar Bin MohamadKhairul Anuar MOHAMAD == References == Category:Malaysian archers Category:Olympians for Malaysia Category:1991 births Category:Living people
